dc_description_s: This data represents addresses for Shawano County, Wisconsin in 2024. [The driveway points are utilized for general mapping purposes and emergency services to locate the main entrance to a parcel. They are used in conjunction with the Driveway line features and building point features. The points were placed using the Planning, Development, and Zoning department's address permit forms and the 2015 orthophotos. Some points were placed with prior orthophotos or placed at the best possible estimate for new construction. Additionally other points have been generated using field work and GPS.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
